      "description": "Before you begin, make the Zingy Green Miso Salmon batch recipe."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Fill a saucepan with water and bring to the boil. Cook the noodles following pack instructions. Once cooked, rinse well under cold running water to chill and remove excess starch."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Toast the sesame seeds in a dry frying pan over a medium heat for a minute or two, until golden and fragrant."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add the tahini, nori, soy sauce, ice cubes and rice vinegar to a blender. Blitz until smooth and creamy – the nori should be fully incorporated. Taste and season with salt and a pinch of sugar if it’s too bitter."
